These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bike, jet-ski, boat
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, freelancer, engineer, entrepreneur
1. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
2. the person driving the bike is not the scientist##6
3. the scientist is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person driving the car is on the right of the scientist##1
6. the scientist is not the person driving the jet-ski##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | bike   | boat    | car    | jet-ski |
| Sport      | entrepreneur | scientist | engineer | freelancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, pop, electronic, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting, sailing, climbing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
2. the fan pop is somewhere to the left of the fan electronic##5
3. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the fan soul##5
4. the fan pop is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fan electronic##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
7. the fan soul is on the right of the fan reggae##1
8. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the fan reggae##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | pop  | electronic    | reggae | soul    |
| Food       | climbing | weightlifting | sailing  | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, fishing, card-games, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, mexican, brazilian, german
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the pakistani##6
2. the mexican is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
3. the brazilian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the mexican is the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
7. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
8. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the german##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | sudoku       | fishing  | writing  | card-games |
| Job        | brazilian | german | mexican | pakistani  |

