The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, analyst, chef, entrepreneur
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
3. the entrepreneur is not the person who's sport is climbing##6
4. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
5. the chef is on the right of the analyst##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the entrepreneur##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | climbing | basketball | parkour     | skiing |
| Transport   | analyst     | chef    | journalist | entrepreneur    |

