.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, surfing, golf
City: hamburg, venice, paris, prague
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
3. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
4. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person traveling to prague##6
5. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | tennis        | golf | surfing | baseball |
| Transport   | prague | hamburg | venice     | paris   |

