.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, bartender, lawyer, freelancer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, azalea, balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the photographer##1
2. the freelancer is not the person who growsazalea##6
3. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdahlia##5
5. the lawyer is the lawyer##1
6. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
7. the lawyer is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
8. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
9. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | bartender | lawyer    | photographer  | freelancer   |
| Nationality   | balloon-flower  | dahlia | azalea | tulip |

