2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the fan reggae##6
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the fan trance##5
4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan trance##1
7. the fan metal is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
8. the fan punk is somewhere to the right of the fan reggae##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | metal  | trance | reggae    | punk |
| Transport   | rock-climbing | baking | cooking | puzzles  |

