There are 4 different favourite colors: green, lilac, turquise, lavender
1. the firefighter is on the left or right of the nurse##3
2. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5
3. the person who likes turquise is not the dancer##6
4. the scientist is between the person who likes lavender and the dancer##2
5. the dancer is on the left of the scientist##1
6. the person who likes lilac is between the person who likes green and the firefighter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | dancer | scientist    | firefighter | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | green         | lilac | lavender   | turquise     |

