.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
House: wooden, art-deco, cottage, ranch-style
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, whist, bridge
1. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
2. the ranch-style house is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
3. the person playing scrabble is the ranch-style house##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the person playing whist is not the ranch-style house##6
6. the art-deco house is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
7. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
8. the wooden house is on the left of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | wooden  | cottage | art-deco | ranch-style |
| Transport   | whist | mah-jongg     | bridge     | scrabble    |

