4. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who growsazalea##5
5. the alhambra-smoker is between the game-smoker and the person who growszinnia##2
6. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
