2. the person playing poker is the owner of the rat##1
3. the person playing backgammon is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rat##2
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | mouse       | rat | hamster     | guinea-pig     |
| Movie-Genre   | whist | poker       | backgammon | billiard |

