4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person playing billiard and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
6. the person playing billiard is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | go  | mah-jongg | bridge | billiard |
| Sport   | card-games | drawing | cooking   | puzzles |

