4. the art-deco house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
5. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
8. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | cape-cod    | craftsman | farmhouse | art-deco         |
| Sport      | goat | hedgehog | ferret          | bird |

