The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, december, october
1. the person driving the subway is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the tram is the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
7. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2      |       3       |       4       |
| Hobby   | bike  | subway | skateboard         | tram |
| Sport   | june | october  | december | february       |

