.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, light-blue, yellow
City: boston, venice, prague, new-york
1. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
2. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5
3. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is not the person who likes azure##6
5. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes azure and the person who likes lavender##2
6. the person who likes yellow is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to venice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | lavender | light-blue | azure | yellow |
| Pet     | prague  | venice      | boston  | new-york       |

