2. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is not the person traveling to new-york##6
5. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
6. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | new-york | rome | prague      | hannover   |
| Transport   | superhero  | time-travel   | mystery | action |

 